title: Trenden Frasier 3/24: Vine, Cannabis, Voting, Nets, Prince Harry, Jensen Karp

On this edition of Trenden Frasier Jack and Miles discuss how amazing 'Vine' was, NY officials reaching an agreement to legalize cannabis, Mississippi Senator suggesting Sunday voting would offend God, Brooklyn Nets facing Utah Jazz w/o their Big Three, Prince Harry getting a job, and Jensen Karp, Cinnamon Toast Shrimp Man, is a dirtbag?
